title: The Signature Series - Musical Key - Pietropaolo - Prix Italia
description:
Imagine if each key signature had its own personality - if it were a real person! Damiano Pietropaolo has done just that, with marvellous results. Each key is played, with numerous clips of music to serve as an example, and we delve into the life of this "person". The folks in Europe were so impressed, they awarded this the Prix Italia.	

I posted this b4, but there were some omissions. Pleas reseed generously.
